data.description:
Welcome to 841 Magnolia Ridge Drive in beautiful Mandeville, LA. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is nestled on a spacious corner lot with woods behind, offering both privacy and convenience to all that the Northshore has to offer and is only minutes away from the Causeway bridge.  Flood Zone X500!!!! Roof is approximately 3 years old!
The living room is adorned with large windows that let in an abundance of natural light, with cathedral ceiling, & a wood burning fireplace. The adjacent kitchen features staineless steel appliances, granite counters and a large counter height bar for extra seating & entertaining. 
The master suite is a private haven, boasting 2 walk-in closets, high ceilings, and a large primary bathroom with cathedral ceiling, separate sinks, a soaking tub & a separate shower. Three additional bedrooms provide ample space for everyone, and can easily be converted into a home office or a hobby room to suit your needs.
Outside, the corner lot provides plenty of room for outdoor activities and entertaining.
Conveniently located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Magnolia Ridge, this home offers easy access to the causeway bridge, the beautiful lakefront,nearby schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Enjoy the tranquility of Mandeville's  nature trails, the Tammany Trace, parks, and recreational areas, all just a stone's throw away.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours. Schedule your private tour of 841 Magnolia Ridge Drive today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenient living.
